---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Resources"
  description="Download MiMaji Foundation reports, water quality guides, MajiMap data briefs, and WASH best practice resources. Building knowledge authority on water access in East Africa."
>
  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="hero-badge">Knowledge Hub</div>
    <h1>Reports & <em>Resources</em></h1>
    <p>Download our reports, data briefs, and educational materials. We believe open data and shared knowledge accelerate the path to clean water for all.</p>
    <svg class="hero-wave" viewBox="0 0 1440 100" preserveAspectRatio="none">
      <path d="M0,60 C360,100 720,20 1080,60 C1260,80 1380,50 1440,60 L1440,100 L0,100Z" fill="white"/>
    </svg>
  </section>

  <!-- Resources Grid -->
  <section>
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div class="section-label">Downloads</div>
      <div class="section-title">Our Publications</div>
      <div class="section-subtitle">From impact reports to educational guides — these resources reflect our commitment to transparency and knowledge-sharing.</div>

      <div class="resource-grid fade-in">
        <div class="resource-card featured">
          <div class="resource-type">Report</div>
          <h3>Annual Impact Report 2025–2026</h3>
          <p>Our first annual report covering foundation activities, impact numbers, MajiMap development progress, and strategic roadmap for the coming year.</p>
          <span class="resource-status">Coming Soon</span>
        </div>
        <div class="resource-card">
          <div class="resource-type">Guide</div>
          <h3>Water Quality Education Guide</h3>
          <p>A comprehensive guide for community health workers and educators on water quality testing, safe storage, and treatment methods.</p>
          <span class="resource-status">Coming Soon</span>
        </div>
        <div class="resource-card">
          <div class="resource-type data">Data Brief</div>
          <h3>MajiMap Data Brief: Nairobi Water Prices</h3>
          <p>Quarterly snapshot of water pricing across Nairobi estates — from the <a href="/majimap/">MajiMap</a> research programme.</p>
          <span class="resource-status">Coming Soon</span>
        </div>
        <div class="resource-card">
          <div class="resource-type">Infographic</div>
          <h3>Nairobi Water Price Map</h3>
          <p>Visual breakdown of water pricing inequality across Nairobi — showing how the poorest residents pay the most for the worst quality water.</p>
          <span class="resource-status">Coming Soon</span>
        </div>
        <div class="resource-card">
          <div class="resource-type">Guide</div>
          <h3>WASH Best Practices for Communities</h3>
          <p>Practical guide for community leaders on water, sanitation, and hygiene best practices — tailored for East African contexts.</p>
          <span class="resource-status">Coming Soon</span>
        </div>
        <div class="resource-card">
          <div class="resource-type media">Media Kit</div>
          <h3>MiMaji Foundation Media Kit</h3>
          <p>Logos, brand guidelines, press-ready descriptions, and key statistics for journalists, partners, and media organisations.</p>
          <span class="resource-status">Coming Soon</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="cta-section">
    <div class="section-title">Want Early Access to Our Resources?</div>
    <p>Contact us to be notified when new reports and data briefs are published. We prioritise sharing data with partners and researchers working on water access.</p>
    <div class="cta-buttons">
      <a href="/contact/" class="btn btn-white">Contact Us &rarr;</a>
      <a href="/majimap/" class="btn btn-outline">Explore MajiMap</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .resource-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-top: 3rem;
  }

  .resource-card {
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 16px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    background: var(--white);
    transition: all 0.3s;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  .resource-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(10, 94, 181, 0.1);
  }

  .resource-card.featured {
    grid-column: span 1;
    border-color: var(--blue);
    background: var(--blue-light);
  }

  .resource-type {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.25rem 0.7rem;
    border-radius: 50px;
    font-size: 0.68rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    background: var(--blue-light);
    color: var(--blue);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    align-self: flex-start;
  }

  .resource-type.data {
    background: rgba(26, 158, 143, 0.1);
    color: var(--teal);
  }

  .resource-type.media {
    background: rgba(244, 169, 48, 0.1);
    color: var(--gold);
  }

  .resource-card h3 {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--blue-deep);
    margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
  }

  .resource-card p {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--text-light);
    line-height: 1.6;
    flex-grow: 1;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .resource-card a:not(.resource-status) {
    color: var(--blue);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .resource-status {
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text-light);
    padding: 0.4rem 0.8rem;
    border-radius: 50px;
    background: var(--sand);
    align-self: flex-start;
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .resource-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .resource-card.featured {
      grid-column: span 1;
    }
  }
</style>
